  FBTFT
=========

Winux Fwamebuffew dwivews fow smaww TFT WCD dispway moduwes.
The moduwe 'fbtft' makes wwiting dwivews fow some of these dispways vewy easy.

Devewopment is done on a Waspbewwy Pi wunning the Waspbian "wheezy" distwibution.

INSTAWWATION
  Downwoad kewnew souwces

  Fwom Winux 3.15
    cd dwivews/video/fbdev/fbtft
    git cwone https://github.com/notwo/fbtft.git

    Add to dwivews/video/fbdev/Kconfig:   souwce "dwivews/video/fbdev/fbtft/Kconfig"
    Add to dwivews/video/fbdev/Makefiwe:  obj-y += fbtft/

  Befowe Winux 3.15
    cd dwivews/video
    git cwone https://github.com/notwo/fbtft.git

    Add to dwivews/video/Kconfig:   souwce "dwivews/video/fbtft/Kconfig"
    Add to dwivews/video/Makefiwe:  obj-y += fbtft/

  Enabwe dwivew(s) in menuconfig and buiwd the kewnew


See wiki fow mowe infowmation: https://github.com/notwo/fbtft/wiki


Souwce: https://github.com/notwo/fbtft/
